      <title>核能仍难以实现，亚马逊更青睐亚洲可再生能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/amazon-prefers-solar-and-wind-energy-to-nuclear-power-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管全球科技公司已开始研究利用核能发电为能源需求巨大的数据中心供电，但亚马逊公司目前仅考虑利用风能和太阳能为亚洲的项目提供绿色能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/amazon-prefers-solar-and-wind-energy-to-nuclear-power-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克银行利润可能因最低准备金率上调而受到冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/bank-profits-may-take-a-hit-from-czech-minimum-reserve-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了降低自身成本，捷克央行将所谓的最低准备金要求提高了一倍，此举可能会导致银行减少放贷并面临利润下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/bank-profits-may-take-a-hit-from-czech-minimum-reserve-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
